Broad Street na Lagos Island, Lagos, Nigeria, bụ ebe azụmahịa dị n'otu n'ime mpaghara azụmahịa etiti obodo ahụ. N'etiti ndị bi na ya: ụlọ oriri na ọṅụṅụ Bagatelle, Christ Church Cathedral Primary School, Eko Boys High School, Newswatch (Nigeria), na St
